 want to know the funny thing?  The other classes that can use say that monks SHOULD have this cape by that time.  Not that it matters, the cape gives like 60 mana, so monks shouldnt even think about taking this over one of those other classes.<br>       I know this is a lot of crap that i just wrote, i didnt think to make a lot of sense out of it, but i just had to get it off my chest.  Oh, and to you guys talking about randoming on this, you obviously have a long, LONG, time to go before you will get a shot at even seeing this drop.  Anyways, that it for now<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
